Rivers Cadet https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rivers_Cadet 0 Rivers Cadet (1 March 1892 – 1 November 1968) was a French actor. Cadet was born Jean Maurice Large in Paris. He was the brother of Fernand Rivers. Rivers_Cadet ( 1_March_1892 – 1_November_1968 ) was a_French_actor . Cadet was_born Jean_Maurice_Large in Paris . He was the_brother of Fernand_Rivers .
